#DStv403 #eNCA JOHANNESBURG - Struggle stalwart Cheryl Carolus has thanked everyone involved in the State Capture Commission. She says they worked hard to uncover the roots of corruption. READ: Corruption is a threat to democracy, says Rev Chikane Carolus spoke at the Defend our Democracy conference on Saturday. She says people implicated by the commission must be held to account. Watch the video above for more details. eNCA's Moloko Mothapo is following this story. Courtesy #DStv403 